General Information

Type.................: OS

Burn Tested..........: Yes

The final version of the series
Last public build for this year.

Release Notes

ssWPI replaced completely by WPI due to technical issues.
Extra reboots removed, installs faster, Visual C++ runtimes moved to WPI.
Driver Pack AIO added to WPI. WINPE to launch Build setup removed.
Setup reverted to normal boot.wim.

Install Notes

Critical Updates to July 15th integrated
Included Simplix Pack to update Live Win7 Build R2-14.7.15 R2 (takes a while to install but its like a service pack).
